data.description: Wonderful single family home for sale in Lone Pine Estates, located close to the VA Hospital, freeway access, close to downtown WPB and the airport. 3/2 with an additional room that can be converted into a 4th bedroom. 2 car garage. Directly on the former Lone Pine golf course, no neighbors behind the home!  Fenced yard and nicely updated inside. All impact windows. Air Conditioner installed 2019
